  <brief_title>Package of Interventions After Recovering From Moderate Acute Malnutrition</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial of the Impact of Offering a Nutrition and Health Intervention to Children Recovered From Moderate Acute Malnutrition</official_title>
